cs.DC, cs.PF, cs.SY, cs.NI, cs.DS 

This paper deals with load balancing in data centers, which is a topic related to distributed computing (cs.DC). It also involves optimization algorithms (cs.PF) and system modeling (cs.SY). The concept of data locality is related to network infrastructure (cs.NI) and the paper discusses the performance of different algorithms, which is related to data structures and algorithms (cs.DS).
